name: Unidentified F'n Objects (64x64 UFO Game Jam)
name_original: Unidentified F'n Objects (64x64 UFO Game Jam)
description:
Earth has been destroyed, and you are the last remaining human. Unidentified F'n Objects came out of the sun, and are blowing up everything in the solar system. You have only 1 goal: survive as long as you can!

CONTROLS

Gamepad: Twin stick to move and aim, right button to fire

or

Keyboard/Mouse: WASD to move, mouse to aim, left button to fire

Important: There is no one left to give you medals for courage - so flying into the sun or through the asteroid belt - while very brave - is not advisable!

This small game was created for the 2016 64x64 game jam. Have fun!
